Mishqah Parthiephal (a mụrụ na 21 Septemba 1989) bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri na South Africa, ihe nlereanya na onye na-emepụta ihe nkiri

Mgbe ọ rụchara ọrụ ihe nkiri mbụ ya n'afọ 2010, ọ rụrụ ọrụ na telivishọn na mgbasa ozi ruo n'afọ 2015. N'èzí South Africa, a maara ya nke ọma maka ọrụ ya dịka onye ọka iwu Priya Seghal na usoro CTV / Netflix The Indian Detective
A mụrụ ya ma zụlite ya na Verulam, n'ebe ugwu Durban, Parthiepal bụ onye Alakụba sitere na India n'akụkụ nna ya na Malay n'akụkụ nne ya. Ọ gara Durban Girls' High School
Ọ gụrụ ihe nkiri na mgbasa ozi na Mahadum KwaZulu-Natal tupu ọ kwaga Johannesburg.
